# Crush Adapter

Read root `AGENTS.md` and `.ai/INDEX.md`.

Set `adapters.crush.model` in `mivia-agent.yaml` for the default provider/model name.
Set `adapters.crush.params` for provider settings such as `provider` or `base_url`.

Crush is guidance-only here. `mivia-agent run` does not orchestrate Crush until a documented headless contract exists.
